<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Investment Plan Invitation</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px 0;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .logo {
        max-width: 150px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .content {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .plan-details {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .plan-details table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
      }
      .plan-details td {
        padding: 8px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      }
      .plan-details td:first-child {
        font-weight: bold;
        width: 40%;
      }
      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #4caf50;
        color: white !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Special Investment Opportunity</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <%= userName %>,</p>

      <p>
        We hope this email finds you well. As a valued member of our platform,
        we're excited to share a special investment opportunity that we believe
        would be a great fit for your investment portfolio.
      </p>

      <div class="plan-details">
        <h3><%= planName %></h3>
        <table>
          <tr>
            <td>Plan Type:</td>
            <td><%= planType %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Investment Range:</td>
            <td><%= minAmount %> - <%= maxAmount %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>ROI:</td>
            <td><%= roi %>%</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Duration:</td>
            <td><%= duration %></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>

      <p>
        This exclusive plan offers competitive returns and is available for a
        limited time. We've selected you based on your previous investment
        activities and believe this opportunity aligns with your financial
        goals.
      </p>

      <p>
        To learn more about this plan or to start investing, simply click the
        button below:
      </p>

      <div style="text-align: center">
        <a href="<%= planUrl %>" class="cta-button">View Plan Details</a>
      </div>

      <p>
        If you have any questions about this investment opportunity, please
        don't hesitate to contact our support team.
      </p>

      <p>Thank you for your continued trust in our platform.</p>

      <p>
        Best regards,<br />
        The ExNestrade Team
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        This email was sent to you because you're a registered user on our
        platform. If you believe this was sent in error, please contact support.
      </p>
      <p>
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> ExNestrade. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
